---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Usage Disclosure - zenxhunger"
  description="Transparency about AI-human collaboration in content creation"
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8">
      AI-Human Collaboration Disclosure
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This website represents an authentic collaboration between human creativity and AI assistance.
          I believe in transparent disclosure of AI usage while maintaining the integrity of original thinking.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
          AI tools serve as thought partners—helping articulate ideas, structure arguments,
          and refine expression. However, the core insights, experiences, and perspectives remain
          fundamentally human.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">How AI is Used</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Content Refinement:</strong> Improving clarity, structure, and readability of written content</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Research Assistance:</strong> Gathering background information and synthesizing technical concepts</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Code Generation:</strong> Creating examples, prototypes, and technical demonstrations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Ideation:</strong> Brainstorming connections across disciplines and exploring concepts</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">What Remains Human</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">●</span>
            <span><strong>Original Perspectives:</strong> All opinions, interpretations, and critical analyses are my own</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">●</span>
            <span><strong>Personal Experience:</strong> Reflections on books, projects, and learning journeys are authentic</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">●</span>
            <span><strong>Editorial Judgment:</strong> Final decisions on content, tone, and direction remain human-driven</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">●</span>
            <span><strong>Curation:</strong> Selection of topics, books, and research areas reflects personal taste</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Commitment to Transparency</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          When specific content is substantially AI-generated (beyond editing and refinement),
          I will explicitly note this in the post's metadata or author notes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
          This disclosure page will be updated as my practices evolve and new tools emerge.
          The goal is always honest representation of the creative process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg p-6 mt-12">
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 italic mb-2">
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
          Questions or feedback about AI usage? Feel free to reach out.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
